name: Fraction Calculator
tagline: A simple calculator for mathematical fractions that supports addition, subtraction, multiplication and division
body:
### What this is
It's a simple calculator to perform simple fraction-based calculations. Made for a school assignment.

### Authors and Contributors
Made for a school assignment by [Hendrik Rombach](https://github.com/hrombach) and [Fabian Lehmann](https://github.com/Gypsyy)

### Support or Contact
Reach me at h.rombach1@gmail.com
